</tr>
<tr>
<td colspan="2" class="" style="text-align:center; padding:0; line-height:1.2em; vertical-align:middle;">Military commission to try Plaintiff is illegal and lacking the protections required under the Geneva Conventions and United States Uniform Code of Military Justice.</td>
